      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains composed with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and sharp steering rack feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring this high-revving masterpiece is mechanically sound and ready for the circuit or the canyon roads.",
